            <article class="deng-home-node-card deng-home-node-card--online">
              <div class="deng-home-node-card__head">
                <span class="deng-home-node-card__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Inventory Sync</h3>
              </div>
              <p>Upload and monitor backpacks with live poll refresh.</p>
              <a class="deng-home-node-link" href="/login">Open inventory →</a>
            </article>
            <article class="deng-home-node-card deng-home-node-card--online">
              <div class="deng-home-node-card__head">
                <span class="deng-home-node-card__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Auto Rejoin</h3>
              </div>
              <p>Keep Roblox sessions alive with configured agents.</p>
              <a class="deng-home-node-link" href="/download">Visit agent →</a>
            </article>
            <article class="deng-home-node-card deng-home-node-card--online">
              <div class="deng-home-node-card__head">
                <span class="deng-home-node-card__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>License Panel</h3>
              </div>
              <p>Manage keys, access, and authorized devices.</p>
              <a class="deng-home-node-link" href="/login">Manage license →</a>
            </article>
            <article class="deng-home-node-card deng-home-node-card--online">
              <div class="deng-home-node-card__head">
                <span class="deng-home-node-card__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Monitor</h3>
              </div>
              <p>Track connected devices, bridge status, and health.</p>
              <a class="deng-home-node-link" href="/login">Open monitor →</a>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
